\begin_inset Formula $OA$
\end_inset

 starting from 
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

.
 This point, then, is said to represent the positive integer, 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
