\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 times the unit length 
\begin_inset Formula $OA$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

This point represents the negative integer, 
\begin_inset Formula $-m$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

