\begin_inset Formula $mq/np$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This is a contradiction.
 Hence 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 cannot correspond to a rational number.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Thus we see that there exist an unlimited number of points on the number-axis
